<eventtime>2005-04-24 12:24:00</eventtime>
<logtime>2005-04-24 11:40:00</logtime>
<subject>Crazy Night!</subject>
<event>Free House generally equals party. But this party went out of control. I knew it would from the minute loads of spides arrived. It was fine for a while, they did their thing, we continued drinking. Then they started smokin in the house, singing sectarian songs, starting fights, being generally abusive and just being everywhere. 

Then some guy was found lying in the bathroom with his boxers down at his ankles. Took him over an hour to get him out of the house and on the grass. Then someone else was sick - then his dad came. Once the chaos of the paralytic kid was over the spides disappeared. The rest of us got mops, gloves, buckets and hoover and proceeded to clean the house. We also tried to apologise to the neighbour... but she wasnt having any of it. 

Eventually, we got some food and watched a movie. I got 3 hrs sleep on the sofa. Got home at 8, then got another 4hrs. 

Theres really something deeply depressing about hanging out with kids younger than me. And all those damn couples...</event>
